url=http://www.irma.ie/best-of-singles|website=IRMA|publisher=IRMA \u2013 Irish Recorded Music Association|accessdate=19 March 2016}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|20\n|-\n|Netherlands (Dutch Top 40)<ref>{{cite web|title=Top 100-Jaaroverzicht van 2008|url=http://www.top40.nl/bijzondere-lijsten/top-100-jaaroverzichten/2008|website=Dutch Top 40|publisher=Stichting Nederlandse Top 40|accessdate=19 March 2016|language=Dutch}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|2\n|-\n|Netherlands (Single Top 100)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://dutchcharts.nl/jaaroverzichten.asp?year=2008&cat=s|title=Jaaroverzichten \u2013 Single 2008|publisher=MegaCharts|language=Dutch|accessdate=24 March 2020}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|6\n|-\n|Sweden (Sverigetopplistan)<ref>{{cite web |title=\u00c5rslista Singlar - \u00c5r 2008 |url=http://www.sverigetopplistan.se/netdata/ghl002.mbr/lista?liid=43&dfom=20080101&newi=0&mode=list&navi=no&platform=Win32&browser=MSIE |website=Sverigetopplistan |publisher=Gramophone Suppliers Association |accessdate=25 March 2016 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6gGKlhD7A |archivedate=25 March 2016 |language=Swedish |url-status=dead |df=dmy-all }}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|16\n|-\n|Switzerland (Schweizer Hitparade)<ref>{{cite web|title=Schweizer Jahreshitparade 2008|url=http://www.hitparade.ch/charts/jahreshitparade/2008|website=Hitparade|publisher=Hung Medien|accessdate=19 March 2016|language=German}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|16\n|-\n|UK Singles (Official Charts Company)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ukchartsplus.co.uk/ChartsPlusYE2008.pdf |title=Official Singles Chart 2008 |accessdate=21 December 2011}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|25\n|-\n|US ''Billboard'' Hot 100<ref>{{cite web|title=Hot 100 Songs - Year End 2008|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2008/hot-100-songs|website=Billboard|publisher=Billboard|accessdate=19 March 2016}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|13\n|-\n|US Adult Contemporary (''Billboard'')<ref>{{cite web|title=Adult Contemporary Songs - Year End 2008|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2008/hot-adult-contemporary-songs|website=Billboard|publisher=Billboard|accessdate=19 March 2016}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|18\n|-\n|US Adult Top 40 (''Billboard'')<ref>{{cite web|title=Adult Pop Songs - Year End 2008|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2008/hot-adult-pop-songs|website=Billboard|publisher=Billboard|accessdate=19 March 2016}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|8\n|}\n\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n!Chart (2009)\n!Position\n|-\n|Australia (ARIA)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.aria.com.au/pages/aria-charts-end-of-year-charts-top-100-singles-2009.htm |title=ARIA Charts \u2013 End Of Year Charts \u2013 Top 100 Singles 2009 |publisher=ARIA |accessdate=12 November 2010}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|92\n|-\n|Austria (\u00d63 Austria Top 40)<ref>{{cite web|title=Jahreshitparade Singles 2009|url=http://www.austriancharts.at/year.asp?cat=s&id=2009|website=Austrian Charts|publisher=Hung Medien|accessdate=20 March 2016|language=German}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|75\n|-\n|Belgium (Ultratop Flanders)<ref>{{cite web|title=Jaaroverzichten 2009|url=http://www.ultratop.be/nl/annual.asp?year=2009|website=Ultratop|publisher=Ultratop & Hung Medien|accessdate=19 March 2016|language=Dutch}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|40\n|-\n|Belgium (Ultratop Wallonia)<ref>{{cite web|title=Rapports Annuels 2009|url=http://www.ultratop.be/fr/annual.asp?year=2009|website=Ultratop|publisher=Ultratop & Hung Medien|accessdate=19 March 2016|language=French}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|48\n|-\n|Canada (Canadian Hot 100)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2009/canadian-hot-100?begin=21&order=position|title=Canadian Hot 100 Year-End 2009|accessdate=2012-03-29}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|21\n|-\n|Germany (Official German Charts)<ref>{{cite web|title=Top 100 Single-Jahrescharts 2009|