yle=\"text-align:center;\"|55\n|-\n|US Adult Contemporary (''Billboard'')<ref>{{cite web|title=Adult Contemporary Songs - Year End 2009|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2009/hot-adult-contemporary-songs|website=Billboard|publisher=Billboard|accessdate=19 March 2016}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|5\n|-\n|Venezuela Pop Rock (Record Report)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.recordreport.com.ve/publico/?i=poprock |title=Pop Rock|language=Spanish|publisher=Record Report|date=2008-08-16| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080816013400/http://www.recordreport.com.ve/publico/?i=poprock|archivedate=2008-08-16}}</ref>\n|align=\"center\"|1\n|}\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!Chart (2011)\n!Position\n|-\n|UK Singles (Official Charts Company)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ukchartsplus.co.uk/UKChartsPlusEOY2011.pdf|title=UK Singles Year-End 2011|accessdate=2008-06-28}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|196\n|}\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!Chart (2016)\n!Position\n|-\n| US Hot Rock Songs (''Billboard'')<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2016/hot-rock-songs |title=Hot Rock Songs \u2013 Year-End 2016 |work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]] |accessdate=19 January 2018}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|80\n|}\n\n===Decade-end charts===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n!Chart (2000\u20132009)\n!Position\n|-\n|Australia (ARIA)<ref>{{cite web|title=2000sDecadeChartssingles|url=http://www.aria.com.au/pages/documents/2000sDecadeChartssingles.pdf|website=ARIA|publisher=ARIA|accessdate=20 March 2016}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|71\n|-\n|Austria (\u00d63 Austria Top 40)<ref>{{cite web|title=Bestenlisten \u2013 00er-Single|url=http://austriancharts.at/00er_single.asp|website=Austrian Charts|publisher=Hung Medien|accessdate=20 March 2016|language=German}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|31\n|-\n|Netherlands (Dutch Top 40)<ref>{{cite web|title=Decenniumlijst: 00's|url=http://www.top40.nl/bijzondere-lijsten/decenniumlijst-00-s|website=Dutch Top 40|publisher=Stichting Nederlandse Top 40|accessdate=20 March 2016|language=Dutch}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|2\n|-\n|US ''Billboard'' Hot 100<ref>{{cite web|title=Hot 100 Songs \u2013 Decade End Charts|url=http://www.billboard.com/bbbiz/charts/decadeendcharts/2009/hot100-songs|website=Billboard|publisher=Billboard|accessdate=20 March 2016|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121020173024/http://www.billboard.biz/bbbiz/charts/decadeendcharts/2009/hot100-songs|archivedate=20 October 2012}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|49\n|}\n\n===All-time charts===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n!Chart\n!Position\n|-\n|Belgium (Ultratop Flanders)<ref>{{cite web|title=Top Aller Tijden \u2013 Singles|url=http://www.ultratop.be/nl/bestall.asp|website=Ultratop|publisher=Ultratop & Hung Medien|accessdate=20 March 2016|language=Dutch}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|75\n|-\n|Netherlands (Dutch Top 40)<ref>{{cite web|title=Nummer 1 Top 40|url=http://www.top40.nl/bijzondere-lijsten/best-scorende-nummer-1-hits|website=Dutch Top 40|publisher=Stichting Nederlandse Top 40|accessdate=20 March 2016|language=Dutch}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|9\n|-\n|Sweden (Sverigetopplistan)<ref>{{cite web|title=Best of All Time \u2013 Singles |url=http://www.swedishcharts.com/bestall.asp |website=Swedish Charts |publisher=Hung Medien |accessdate=25 March 2016 |language=Swedish |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070221151820/http://www.swedishcharts.com/bestall.asp |archivedate=21 February 2007 }}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|44\n|-\n|Switzerland (Schweizer Hitparade)<ref>{{cite web|title=Ewige Bestenliste \u2013 Singles|url=http://hitparade.ch/charts/best/singles|website=Hitparade|publisher=Hung Medien|accessdate=20 March 2016|language=German}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|39\n|-\n|US ''Billboard'' Hot 100<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/charts/hot-100-60th-anniversary|title=Billboard Hot 1